---
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
---

<section class="box skills">
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="terminal-window"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Full Stack</h2>
    <p>
      Experienced Developer adept at navigating diverse web frameworks. Seamless
      integration with server, mobile, and desktop developments. A collaborative
      team player, ready to contribute and enhance project dynamics.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon icon="trophy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
    <h2>Industry Leader</h2>
    <p>
      Skilled in project management and planning. Committed to mentoring and
      guiding emerging developers. Thrives in leadership roles, ensuring project
      success through collaboration and strategic vision. Pursuing greatness
      together is the key.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="strategy"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Strategy-Minded</h2>
    <p>
      A strategic problem solver in software development, I excel in unraveling
      complexities to deliver optimized solutions. My approach blends deep
      technological understanding with a focus on efficiency and code
      optimization. 
	  <!-- Bringing strategic insight to your projects, I am committed
      to driving technological innovation and problem-solving. -->
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .box {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .skills h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  .skills p {
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .box {
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5rem;
    }

    .skills h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }
  }
</style>
